  "info" : {
    "title" : "Avalon Game API",
    "description" : "Game, lobby and user endpoints served by avalon-spring, consumed by the Avalon KMP client (contract-first via kmpgen).\n\nAuth is handled upstream by the ForwardAuth service: the client sends `Authorization: Bearer <jwt>` on every call, the gateway validates it and injects the `Avalon-Header-Logged-In-User-Username` header. That header is therefore omitted from this contract (the client never sets it), and avalon-spring itself declares no security scheme.",
    "version" : "0.1.0"
  },
